Additional Warranty Disclaimer for Document Processing:

THE SOFTWARE PROVIDES DOCUMENT PROCESSING CAPABILITIES WITHOUT ANY WARRANTY
REGARDING THE ACCURACY OF OPTICAL CHARACTER RECOGNITION (OCR), DOCUMENT
ANALYSIS, OR DATA EXTRACTION. USERS MUST INDEPENDENTLY VERIFY ALL EXTRACTED
INFORMATION AND MAINTAIN APPROPRIATE QUALITY CONTROL PROCESSES.

Security Incident Notification:

USERS MUST NOTIFY THE COPYRIGHT HOLDERS WITHIN 72 HOURS OF ANY SECURITY
INCIDENTS OR BREACHES INVOLVING THE SOFTWARE THAT MAY IMPACT THE
CONFIDENTIALITY, INTEGRITY, OR AVAILABILITY OF PROTECTED DOCUMENTS OR
SENSITIVE INFORMATION.